"pid":"4c8805489a56f823798b37d944b1665d24bcf563","tid":100432,"uid":20347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"痾清嘔清就淨係食白粥同藥 第二日即刻行得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56e674a7fd562ba8032fdd108b9766e402a8b79","tid":100432,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係飲寶礦力其他咩都唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋喇叭丸止屙都幾有用</blockquote><br />\n驚樓主食藥都會頂住個胃</blockquote><br />\n喇叭牌唔掂<br />\n佢真係幫你止痾嘔<br />\n但係你腸胃炎唔痾清就好唔返<br />\n如果真係要食中成藥就食李萬山整腸丸"},{"pid":"d7bc0d94826966bb36f5a734c6bf0b25da81ffea","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢幾日加埋到底有幾多個腸胃炎POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗應該係維園啲野食搞到咁</blockquote><br />\n戎左掃街啦 街邊小食真係唔乾淨 <br />\n腸胃弱小小都奶哂野</blockquote><br />\n諗住一年一次咪食下 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb536bf0277c4b2e94ef413ce377a3741fdc746","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間表呢？</blockquote><br />\n冇乜留意幾時一次   可唔可以解釋多小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b9e9d08ee973e267b56af54c61cd98eea48dc8","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生未？</blockquote><br />\n初一入咗急症 之後醫生開咗啲藥比我 好似唔冇效咁"},{"pid":"95a0339c3633433cdfdc519c5343e308c855f746","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係飲寶礦力其他咩都唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋喇叭丸止屙都幾有用</blockquote><br />\n驚樓主食藥都會頂住個胃</blockquote><br />\n喇叭牌唔掂<br />\n佢真係幫你止痾嘔<br />\n但係你腸胃炎唔痾清就好唔返<br />\n如果真係要食中成藥就食李萬山整腸丸</blockquote><br />\n其實我都驚亂食藥會越食越衰 只係敢食醫生開嗰啲藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b864d62fbe24f00b81fc8ce7d594b8736d093917","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期嘔到食完藥都即刻嘔返出來<br />\n都係飲保礦力<br />\n今年好似好多人中招</blockquote><br />\n啱啱都差啲嘔番啲藥出黎 好彩忍得住唔係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95476adae80eb21951536cfb3e120063918ec535","tid":100432,"uid":10674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"依家放屁都驚咇屎出黎<br />\n痾緊水"},{"pid":"d857a711e47bad49893b89b2ad8880bd4baffc5f","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痾清嘔清就淨係食白粥同藥 第二日即刻行得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有巴打都話食粥 我上網搵過佢地又話可能會有反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5aa9f86f32fffa1f99998211aa86a7e7979dc0c","tid":100432,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生未？</blockquote><br />\n初一入咗急症 之後醫生開咗啲藥比我 好似唔冇效咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸胃炎都入急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b70417981c1dc5243597e0d614a7daf2ac4d506","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家放屁都驚咇屎出黎<br />\n痾緊水</blockquote><br />\n巴打你都同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"0e32d98ff342438c016331fc5f9ce41dba489baf","tid":100432,"uid":47819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"其實all 完嘔完真係無事。睇你頂唔頂得順<br />\n再食番清淡d好快會好番"},{"pid":"5c11e49d8515efa572eb6dc256f5fe252645889e","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生未？</blockquote><br />\n初一入咗急症 之後醫生開咗啲藥比我 好似唔冇效咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸胃炎都入急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一直都頭暈身㷫 個時想去睇醫生但唔記得新年休息 之後諗住過幾日先再睇 瞓咗陣起身仲暈 打999之後入咗急症 暈都唔知自己發緊高燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d270bd7d0b3462731fafb34d37f4b1c7bb5f19a9","tid":100432,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"屙左第五日 好似就好番 琴日仲偷食m記"},{"pid":"23b12903077ecddbd7f7f11c30315d3f1d524081","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實all 完嘔完真係無事。睇你頂唔頂得順<br />\n再食番清淡d好快會好番</blockquote><br />\n頂就頂得順 明明好餓但一食野真係一啖起兩啖止"},{"pid":"ee8b818ba6838a1241fffe3489cde67f873f53d3","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屙左第五日 好似就好番 琴日仲偷食m記</blockquote><br />\n其實我都好想食脆香雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c786304eb36c490eea37327498605e82f48e882c","tid":100432,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n初一入咗急症 之後醫生開咗啲藥比我 好似唔冇效咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸胃炎都入急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一直都頭暈身㷫 個時想去睇醫生但唔記得新年休息 之後諗住過幾日先再睇 瞓咗陣起身仲暈 打999之後入咗急症 暈都唔知自己發緊高燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你等左幾耐<br />\n等待期間唔使去洗手間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad198ad245245f36b2b13b0d3fc5b24bfa4d1dff","tid":100432,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸胃炎都入急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一直都頭暈身㷫 個時想去睇醫生但唔記得新年休息 之後諗住過幾日先再睇 瞓咗陣起身仲暈 打999之後入咗急症 暈都唔知自己發緊高燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你等左幾耐<br />\n等待期間唔使去洗手間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等咗1個鐘左右 唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為太攰成個人冇力所以都係瞓覺多"},{"pid":"88273297bf4e1d34bbcffd324048348f4978c918","tid":100432,"uid":71369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"仆街，我都賴賴地野，想痾嘔但又嘔唔出，胃脹又定住，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過我腸胃不嬲都好差，記得戒口，唔好偷食其他野，有咁清得咁清"},{"pid":"d065bb001247b24fd4f9523d2b5822245db1df16","tid":100432,"uid":10674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T10:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家放屁都驚咇屎出黎<br />\n痾緊水</blockquote><br />\n巴打你都同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n琴日痛到個胃扭毛巾咁<br />\n今日先好返d<br />\n想嘔又嘔唔出<br />\n衰為食<br />\n我夠膽講腸胃炎慘過食屎"}]}